    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>I would prefer:</p>\n\n<pre><code>try\n{\n    ...\n}\ncatch (FooException fe){\n   throw fe;\n}\ncatch (Exception e)\n{\n    // Note: don't catch all exceptions like this unless you know what you\n    // are doing.\n    ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
