    "question_id" : 1097527,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>something like this</p>\n\n<pre><code>try \n{\n  ...\n}\ncatch (FooException e) \n{\n  throw e;\n}\ncatch (Exception e)\n{\n  ...\n}\n</code></pre>\n"
