      "post_id" : 58952645,
      "comment_id" : 127443225,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Avoid self-made extraction of info about <code>e</code>. Better pack the original exception with <code>throw new RuntimeException(&quot;Some usefull info&quot;, e)</code>. In the string, gives somes usefull info that are missing in <code>e</code>, for example some important arguments of your method, info about the context, or whatever will help debugging."
